      <section eId="section_9">
        <heading><b>Annex A – Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></heading>
        <paragraph>
          <num>598 </num>
          <content>
            <p>This Act extends and applies to the whole of the UK. In addition, repeals and amendments made by the Act have the same territorial extent and application as the legislation that they are repealing or amending. </p>
          </content>
        </paragraph>
      </section>
